name: Ad Nauseam
description:
Words regurgitated,
I’ve hit a plateau.
Not even a single speck of dust
lands
on its fine surface.
 
Delusional;
mind dulled in vacancy.
I’ve grown complacent
with empty responses.
 
It’s as if
I can’t remember
how to feel.
 
There is a knot that
resides within my chest.
Its noose
constricting my airway.
 
I’ve become the gray ocean waves
that continue to lap,
as the cool solemn winds
make peace with my soul.
